<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Damsel" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Damsel,</orth> lass, wench: <cit><quote>it was a spite unto the silly d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 218" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 218</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I was taken with a d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.292" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 292</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.292" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 292</bibl> 294 (Ff Q<hi rend="sub">2</hi> <emph>damosell</emph>). <cit><quote>for this d., I must keep her at the park,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.135" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 135</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d., I'll have a bout with you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.56" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 56</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. of France, I think I have you fast,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.30" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 30</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>